{"tid":1634561,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有人問點解依幾日都要開花 ？","createTime":"2019-10-07T08:39:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T08:47:25.000Z","uid":250061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"eb827ae6c9f247cfa7997c807092ba381bed5344","tid":1634561,"uid":250061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:39:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">依幾日更加要開</span></span><br />\n<br />\n近幾日唔少屌鬼posts都係講最近做得有冇過火，但係說好的<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">不分化 不割蓆</span></span>？<br />\n<br />\n勇武每次出去裝修 火魔法我都好支持，但最近真係少左文宣去解釋返依幾日既行動。政府突然推得咁急點解？因為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">民主及人權法案</span></span>就過。想你們係無輿論 文宣嘅支持下出黎反對 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">等你們出師無名</span></span><br />\n<br />\n政府想我們變得激進 更亂 失去理性，務求幫你地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">形象大改造</span></span>，令你們無論係淺黃 中立 甚至外國眼中都覺得示威者形象變差 已經失去原本嘅初衷 甚至理性<br />\n<br />\n正因為咁樣 我們更加要把握依幾日時間用另類形式開花 鍾意唱歌就唱歌 做文宣就做文宣。去解釋近期我們行動目的 把矛頭轉向政府 <br />\n<br />\n所以唔單只要有本土戰線支持 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">外國戰線好緊要</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n冇外國方面嘅支持 場運動一早玩完 冇本土200萬300萬人支持 場運動一樣玩完 冇和理非同勇武配合 場運動已 end game <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">明白依段時間大家都難免受風向影響 但記住我哋同藍絲唔同嘅係 我哋有理性 有獨立思考</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">記住 五大訴求 缺一不可 先係本心</span></span>"},{"pid":"6524c325a7a59f7dabe75d9eb251146c67b89c4e","tid":1634561,"uid":250061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:40:28.000Z","msg":"手機排版 屌細力d"},{"pid":"f7e93d0ecf5b202de7f55a438641fdc706176ccb","tid":1634561,"uid":182774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:40:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4bb0b28e7668f3e956be41c675c130da08d1f071","tid":1634561,"uid":250061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:40:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5872379622b503864af2e5d75856745c2a1d5e83","tid":1634561,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:41:16.000Z","msg":"休息撚進場"},{"pid":"cdd35b60a1adaa6d3c17eb8b89c34266c96713ec","tid":1634561,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:42:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c99f46d3f815d2353dc01a5ffa055907060da4","tid":1634561,"uid":250061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:43:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d0650e82e23f8b89f215c6c2df0f30cbaec402ae","tid":1634561,"uid":47659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:43:24.000Z","msg":"總之<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今晚唔休息<br />\n18區要人</span></span><br />\n<br />\ngphone作為sell法案既先導者, 已經叫左大家唔好割裝修/魔法, 因為法案無可能7日通過, 通過亦唔代表有實際壓力可以令我地即贏.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%97%9C%E6%96%BC-%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E5%BE%9E%E4%BE%86%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E9%90%B5%E6%9D%BF%E4%B8%80%E5%A1%8A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%2596%25BC-%25E8%25A3%259D%25E4%25BF%25AE-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25BE%259E%25E4%25BE%2586%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E6%259D%25BF%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25A1%258A%2F&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn2o8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=fb8476e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%2596%25BC-%25E8%25A3%259D%25E4%25BF%25AE-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25BE%259E%25E4%25BE%2586%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E6%259D%25BF%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25A1%258A%2F&h=7732283f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%97%9C%E6%96%BC-%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E5%BE%9E%E4%BE%86%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E9%90%B5%E6%9D%BF%E4%B8%80%E5%A1%8A/</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>大家緊守崗位，記得四大原則。<br />\n<br />\n10月7日<br />\n<br />\n和理非：<br />\n1. 貼文宣 (全日)<br />\n2. 唱歌 (大家預15:00後)<br />\n3. 追悼會 (19:00，睇日程表)<br />\n3. 國際文宣戰線 (全日)<br />\n<br />\n勇武：<br />\n1. 只針對裝修爛鐵(睇赤鐵情況而定，可在20:00或更早)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SXfkVGt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSXfkVGt.jpg&h=cf2461bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2UBoTte.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2UBoTte.jpg&h=916ce106&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0d181ad1cb5fd9656067ffadfb22f3ccc534c5cf","tid":1634561,"uid":250061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:45:52.000Z","msg":"勇武冇做錯 幫佢地解話係和理非責任"},{"pid":"7ffc0786d93cdeb2e3b9a975dd36d94d9c5ff306","tid":1634561,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:46:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a47f3b1b32df5df0e236bd06e528a8da7c05c80","tid":1634561,"uid":250061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:47:25.000Z","msg":"「幫勇武護航」※文宣圖集※<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634078\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634078</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}